{"article_id":"PicVWKDKtiSH1fzJ","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON ( ) -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"U.S. President Donald Trump signed Congress ' newly passed $ 1.3 trillion spending bill on Friday ,","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"ending several hours of confusion","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"spurred by a tweeted veto threat","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"that raised the specter of a government shutdown .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"Trump said","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"he had signed the bill ,","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"despite his qualms on some issues ,","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"because a $ 60 billion increase in military spending had convinced him","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"it was a worthwhile compromise .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"\" But I say to Congress","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"I will never sign another bill like this again , \"","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"he told reporters .","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"\" I ' m not going to do it again . \"","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"White House and Capitol Hill aides had been left scrambling earlier in the day","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"after Trump criticized the six-month spending bill ,","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"despite prior assurances from the administration","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"that he would sign it ahead of a looming midnight deadline .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"\" I am considering a VETO of the Omnibus Spending Bill","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"based on the fact","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"that the 800,000 plus DACA recipients have been totally abandoned by the Democrats","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"( not even mentioned in Bill )","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"and the BORDER WALL ,","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"which is desperately needed for our National Defense ,","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"is not fully funded , \"","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"Trump wrote on Twitter at 9 a.m. EDT .","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"Trump then huddled with his senior advisers","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"to discuss a potential veto","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"and was advised against it ,","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"with the advisers saying","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"he would be blamed for a shutdown","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"and that discussions continue on the issues","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"he is concerned about ,","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"one aide said .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"By early afternoon , he appeared before reporters in the Diplomatic Reception Room of the White House","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"to announce","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"he had signed the measure .","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"\" There are a lot of things","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"I ' m unhappy about in this bill , \"","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"he said ,","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"patting the more than 2,000 pages of the legislation","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"stacked on a purple box beside him .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"U.S. President Donald Trump points to Congress ' $ 1.3 trillion spending bill during a signing ceremony in the Diplomatic Room of the White House in Washington .","depth":5},{"id":43,"text":"U.S. , March 23 , 2018 .","depth":5},{"id":44,"text":"/Kevin Lamarque","depth":4},{"id":45,"text":"It was unclear how seriously Republican leaders took Trump ' s shutdown threat .","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"Neither Speaker Paul Ryan nor Senate Leader Mitch McConnell commented publicly on it .","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"Lawmakers in the Republican-dominated Senate and House of Representatives had already left Washington for a scheduled two-week spring recess ,","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"and Trump himself was scheduled on Friday to fly to Florida for a weekend at his private resort .","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"Trump has been frustrated","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"that Congress has not turned over funding","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"to make good on his campaign promise","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"to build a wall along the U.S.-Mexico border .","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"The bill includes $ 1.6 billion for six month ' s of work on the project","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"but he had sought $ 25 billion for it .","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"Trump also has been at odds with Democrats in Congress over the fate of Dreamer immigrants","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"- those","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"brought to the United States illegally","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"when they were children .","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"Trump canceled the Deferred Action for Childhood Arrivals","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"( DACA )","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"program","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"that gives work permits to the Dreamers","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"and protects them from deportation .","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"The decision is currently tied up in court cases .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"He offered to extend the protections ,","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"tied to a sweeping set of changes to immigration laws ,","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"but subsequently rejected bipartisan offers from lawmakers .","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"As the six-month spending budget deal was coming together ,","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"there had been reports","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"Trump had balked at the bill","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"and had to be persuaded by Ryan to support it .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"The conservative wing of Trump ' s party had panned the bill","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"because of its spending increases","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"and some deficit hawks cheered Trump ' s Friday morning threat","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"to veto it .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":151,"left":0,"right":150,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":150,"left":116,"right":149,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":116,"left":88,"right":115,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":88,"left":79,"right":87,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":7